{"h1544b333g4bd9g4a0fgbf84g4502cf88034e": ["Death by day, death by night, and here we are murdering our own. There's only madness here.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "936beeb4-2c68-d79c-4155-372da97f873e"], "h3a52257eg38dbg4ea3g9390g2d8ceacb49b6": ["Please. We've said enough.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "a77772ba-1fd2-2b84-222b-4efe44600436"], "h532ffb0dgd781g4c9agaf92g2a97a4bb8a69": ["You. Lae'zel. That was brutal.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "0bd05a41-19bc-70af-9b8d-f4cf2ea6915c"], "h556369ccg66c8g4b57gaa27gfd8534e754ae": ["Are you all right? I'm here if you want to talk about it.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "90b14637-fb10-e6d8-9f62-d13141bc461e"], "hffc67098g69a8g4329gb0d2g8de9f15923b5": ["Is there anything left to say?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "c4df526a-8b78-a078-e9ab-7b5d1d769433"], "h7ea94deag2442g4785g9f7ag5c5f9e44b3b4": ["She was alive. Now's she's dead. Might be worth a few words.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "4b3ce1d6-84ab-3aae-38ad-62e9e4d9c16a"], "h43cd5297gcbb0g4c7dgadc7g0742f19b0009": ["Then again, maybe not.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "391bb896-d925-6cd4-499c-440e9382bc6c"], "h0cb85f5bgb56cg4c0bga908gb7b819397609": ["What a night... what a godsdamned...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "c67a56c0-95e4-e337-8ce1-d496af9ec839"], "h74b5bfdegb6c2g42aeg8a2bg02f374749cd6": ["*Cough! Cough!*", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "5d817711-af99-a5a8-66a9-fa034bb580dd"], "he178f730g4235g48e3g8990g45918b0ba8bf": ["More blood. There's a pretty sight.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "83502acb-e2ef-d754-4711-19a3baf45215"], "h8a58c92egc6f3g40bdg90b7g96c9b89789c8": ["Give it to me straight. How do I look?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "11f4c41c-9245-0e4d-9a53-bc3e4f96c2c6"], "h86cfbf46gaa2fg45cfgb105gc7ed83d7c519": ["Like your handsome self, Gale.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "5d770b46-7714-0d68-6090-e096c05ed7d6"], "h9c55c4fcg1725g4239ga411gce093b289e74": ["Thanks. That's what I thought.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "0c2c3940-7850-f090-eaf5-0cefc55fff35"], "h68aeb298gdda8g4644gbd5dga180c50b7da6": ["You don't look so hot either, I might add.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "f11dbd7e-b5eb-671e-a063-3e6f47b83b5d"], "hbd5704bfg89c7g4293g9ae9g23613a6d56ba": ["So either the fish we had was bad, or - or <i>it</i> might just be happening.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "c2e8c766-4c05-5417-6f20-2f3b0bf5b3c0"], "h28e46d9cga3aag4d84gae1fg374ce8b34694": ["We didn't have any fish.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "5606ee13-1c13-806e-1121-d4a1e73fc17d"], "h177f228dgf6e5g423cg800aga185b78aebcc": ["Right.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "96b0075c-eb9e-e48e-046a-a7e2d1fdd0f1"], "ha02f481bgb4f7g47fdg91b1g024f9c20f011": ["I'm going to bed. Sleep, if I can. Find some peace, if that's possible.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "2f5b8493-ac1b-9257-a966-79d73b6622c4"], "he4015166gebc4g48d7gaf14g1750de155e12": ["Meanwhile I'll just pretend I had the fish.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "7840a306-4318-79b4-ac34-1e9662b2dccd"], "h03af80f1g0e00g4d71gbe88gde3a44c233f6": ["A peace different from Laezel's with any luck.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "d30308a2-e936-7796-3749-656ca8eff987"], "h94665502gcf33g4bb2g94b4g35e84ad02320": ["You reckon this is it?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "3b6b7893-6104-b09e-0e63-e779c06355f5"], "hd05bb51cg3993g489dgb15agab55b23cf37b": ["Everything that's been happening to us so far has been most irregular. Who's to say this is not just another anomaly among many?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "acba57f8-471f-4d17-1a2f-c9435cb70d5d"], "h912e672cg232ag48d6g9fe6g197eae0bf2dd": ["My way of saying I haven't a clue.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "132dc7d0-6f76-d58f-62ee-17c1d05589db"], "h668a551bg999ag423fga09fg9cb2ec7fae58": ["Or it might just be nothing. Go to sleep.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "0074feba-3b3e-7ee7-64c4-2bd75d70e35c"], "hbc2fa7f5g3d96g4e39gab57g4b6d8587f9d6": ["So I shall. And dream the dreams of denial.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "80df8272-848e-e80f-d181-8978d3245715"], "hc9fcdeacg3616g4493gae32g87c4dbf6661d": ["We put Lae'zel to bed. Not sure I want to follow her example.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "5609a073-d9c8-7876-8738-d42971f9910b"], "h7a9ad0b2g1244g4b35g8f26gb50372694c61": ["You put Lae'zel to bed. Not sure I want to follow her example.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "a6d08dd7-24a6-d013-ba70-92bdf1dbb9b9"], "h5b662616g4736g40d3gac03g74637eb34996": ["You don't look so hot either, I might add. And neither do the others.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "62607f96-e1a5-9ebe-fc90-e3aa20426b26"], "h61110d4cgb8d4g4db9g87cfgb5a6470ee948": ["Like a dog. As in: 'as sick as'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "b0bc0eb9-da69-43ed-613d-814e2910da39"], "hee1b70d5g10bfg4ba7g9b78g7dba7518ff36": ["Canine as charged.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "bb96df6d-9179-90ea-3085-0eef78fbe7d8"], "h63d9a519g07f1g4835g80e4gbcb6930c3334": ["I'd rather not say.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "f255f774-386b-0ce0-02bf-9c9f448b06e9"], "h3f7eb8c4g7aeag4592ga5e4ga70aec45d8e5": ["Right back at you.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "a83affc2-d13a-4f97-a2d7-2d4ece338475"], "h828f6f9eg487cg4dbdg961egedd442a5d07f": ["Right back at you. And I could say the same of the others.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "a58d3d86-3ca2-91f0-62cd-bd8178bd57f7"], "h26171fbcga94dg4b1egadd1gab5ed04ca5fa": ["Blood. There's a pretty sight.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "e5a66a1f-7aa4-16b5-7b4a-fec66c735614"], "hbe5958ffg1edfg428bgb291g4e5f6c504159": ["She was a danger to us all. She didn't leave me with a choice.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "3c1ef67c-dd7c-7fd9-efc3-00bc1c6470c3"], "h88c9ff62g1cb8g40e6gad34g3e2a4fddca3a": ["I wasn't judging, merely offering my sympathy.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "6ebc14b1-fae1-b395-c653-92647dac5514"], "hcbd347aegd8f6g454bgbbf0g213f61d08ac0": ["One moment we're travelling together, then the next...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "1c4ba0c4-6403-4a8e-142b-72bb5a764ad1"], "h76e2efd8g84efg46fbga78bg5a423c151281": ["It's what she wanted. I merely obliged.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "8e2bac2d-5226-f1b5-748d-dde41ba9fad1"], "h75971493gfcd3g435egae5eg14a9a5b7ff67": ["Not like she asked you to make her a cup of tea exactly.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "b83687b3-7c1f-8413-5c31-fd8a4d95f3ba"], "h737408dbg59fcg481aga0f0gd9f14be1e399": ["Don't bother. It's over and done with.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "fd2bfb80-97cf-194c-cd72-38f946d900f8"], "h4acca273gce5dg4bdcg8b6agec11732b6607": ["Words as final as your acts.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "d629b5d3-2d69-1187-a596-a3b9a17260bd"], "hd5762ea7g5334g450bg863bgf8af9bb97318": ["Lae'zel... That was brutal.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "cbe9c07a-7aa4-95ad-7121-7afbea7c7056"], "h7afc1801g78b1g4f8dga13egfb86c9c963c4": ["What a night... what a godsdamned...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Daisy1_CRD_Gale_BeforeDream.html", "00e64818-3ee3-acf9-c747-a1459e6cfab0"]}